[[File:2009 LPGA Championship - Karrie Webb (2).jpg|thumb|right|upright|150px|alt=A blonde-haired woman in a white hat and light blue shirt holding a golf club at the end of a swing|[[Karrie Webb]] is only one of seven golfers to repeat as champion of the event 2000 and 2001.]]
